org.jsapar.schema

Class SchemaLine

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jsapar.schema.SchemaLine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CsvSchemaLine, FixedWidthSchemaLine

    public abstract class SchemaLine
extends Object
implements Cloneable
    Abstract base class that describes the schema for a line. For instance if you want to ignore a header line you can add a SchemaLine instance to your schema with occurs==1 and ignoreRead==true;
